{"word":"H6960 - קָוָה - qâvâh - kaw-vaw' - Gather","slug":"H6960","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָוָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qâvâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-vaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gather"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D5;&#x05D4; - qa&#x0302;va&#x0302;h</b> - <i>kaw-vaw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>bind</i> together (perhaps by <i>twisting</i>), that is, <i>collect</i>; (figuratively) to <i>expect: - </i>gather (together), look, patiently, tarry, wait (for, on, upon)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4723\">H4723</a>, <a href=\"#/H4724\">H4724</a>"}]}